Detailed Description

Parameters:
pSystemID[OUT] 
  • System ID
  • 0XFFFF,if not available.
pNetworkID[OUT] 
  • Network ID
  • 0XFFFF, if not available.
pBaseStationID[OUT] 
  • Base Station Identification Number
  • 0XFFFF, if not available.
pBaseStationLatitude[OUT] 
  • Base station latitude in units of 0.25 sec,expressed as a
  • two's complement signed number with positive numbers signifying North latitude
  • 0XFFFFFFFF, if not available
pBasestationLongitude[OUT] 
  • Base station longitude in units of 0.25 sec, expressed as a
  • Two's complement signed number with positive numbers signifying East longitude
  • 0XFFFFFFFF, if not available.
pLac[OUT] 
  • Location Area Code
  • 0XFFFF, if not available.
pCellID[OUT] 
  • Cell ID
  • 0XFFFFFFFF, if not available.
p3GppTimeZone[OUT] 
  • Offset from Universal time, i.e., difference between local time and Universal time, in increments of 15 min. (signed value).
GppNetworkDSTAdjustment[OUT] 
  • 3GPP network daylight saving adjustment
    • 0x00 - No adjustment for Daylight Saving Time
    • 0x01 - 1 hr adjustment for Daylight Saving Time
    • 0x02 - 2 hr adjustment for Daylight Saving Time
p3Gpp2TimeZone[OUT] 
  • 3GPP2 Time Zone
  • Further defined by the structure qaQmi3Gpp2TimeZone
